'''Mish'al "Meesh" Samman''' (ID 3973) is the former Commanding Officer of the Saudi Arabian Outpost, part of the real-world [[501st Legion (fan organization)|501st Legion]] costuming organization. His likeness, as drawn by ''[[Star Wars]]'' artist and author [[Jan Duursema]], appears on the last page of [[Legacy (2006) 16|''Legacy'' (2006) 16]] as [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Meeshal]], an [[Imperial officer/Legends|Imperial officer]] under the command of [[Darth Stryfe]].<ref name="FBP">{{WebCite|url=https://www.fanboyplanet.com/comics/mc-mishalstarwars.php|text=A Long Time Ago On A Fanboy Planet Far, Far Away&hellip;|author=Derek McCaw|date=2007-09-13|work=[https://fanboyplanet.com Fanboy Planet]|archivedate=20080906090159|nolive=1}}</ref>

